  "detailed_description": "<strong>Paranormal Place</strong><br>is a first-person psychological thriller. The main emphasis of the game is on the process of exploration, the tension slowly builds up, creating complete and vivid immersive effect.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/56e125158969872e84c69fa17ed226f1.poster.avif?t=1721854424\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/56e125158969872e84c69fa17ed226f1.webm?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/56e125158969872e84c69fa17ed226f1.mp4?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Short description:</strong><br>The main character is a  blogger Alex. He runs his own channel and searches for paranormal trends there. Now he goes to an abandoned buildings, where were military barracks in the past, according to the official information. He takes with him all his devices: a camera and a video surveillance system. <br>You won’t have any doubts about the existence of the other world, after exploring this building. Make content that’ll turn you into an internet star! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/fd9ebb5996439752706651c492160bf1.poster.avif?t=1721854424\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/fd9ebb5996439752706651c492160bf1.webm?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/fd9ebb5996439752706651c492160bf1.mp4?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features of the game:</strong><br>- UE 5.3;<br>- Bodycam effect;<br>- The genre of \"Walking Simulator\";<br>- 3D surround sound;<br>- Realistic graphics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/356c9792e664205d389056ae06e47246.poster.avif?t=1721854424\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/356c9792e664205d389056ae06e47246.webm?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947800/extras/356c9792e664205d389056ae06e47246.mp4?t=1721854424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i><u>Estimated time of walkthrough is 60 minutes.</u></i></strong><br><br> <u><strong>DESCRIPTION OF CONTENT FOR ADULTS</strong></u><br>The developer describes the content as follows:<br>The game contains realistic depictions of violent scenes that can have a negative impact on the psyche. Some content may be inappropriate for certain age groups.",
